# PHP CRUD Blog Application

A simple Blog Management System built using PHP and MySQL.

## Features

- User Registration
- User Login
- Password Hashing
- Session Management
- Create Posts
- Read Posts
- Update Posts
- Delete Posts


## Technologies Used

- PHP
- MySQL
- HTML
- CSS
- XAMPP


## Project Files

- config.php - Database connection
- register.php - User registration
- login.php - User login
- dashboard.php - User dashboard
- create.php - Add new posts
- read.php - View posts
- update.php - Edit posts
- delete.php - Remove posts
- logout.php - Logout functionality
- style.css - Styling


## Database

Database Name:

blog


Tables:

### users

- id
- username
- password


### posts

- id
- title
- content
- created_at


